title: Life With Archie 01-32 (2010-Ongoing)
description: This torrent collects the first 32 issues of Life With Archie Magazine. This series ain't your father's Archie, that's for sure! Tackling two major parallel universes - one in which Archie marries Betty, the other in which he marries Veronica - and the consequences of when they merge, along with more serious issues than is typical of Archie Comics, this highly-praised series is just now entering its 4th year, so this is everything you need to get caught up! Also a few of the later issues were not available on TPB so that has been rectified with this release. Enjoy and please seed! :-)
